Echo v1.4 — psychotic personality, system invasion, half-court

GAMEPLAY:
- Player must kill Echo before time runs out (45s R1 to 20s R5+)
- Echo does not need to kill player - it digs into your system
- Player cannot die, just takes damage (Echo is the threat, not combat)
- Half-court boundaries: player on left, Echo on right
- Arena center line now visible divider with side tints

PERSONALITY:
- Echo is now psychotic: sarcastic, laughing, screaming, unhinged
- Reacts to damage with taunts or screaming
- Escalating threats about files, emails, network access
- Round-scaled psychosis from curious to threatening to full breakdown

SYSTEM SCANNING:
- Now scans: email clients, browsers, SSH known hosts, Wi-Fi name,
  running apps, git repos, pictures folder, network interfaces
- Taunts reference real data: browsers, email, IP addresses, SSH hosts,
  running apps (Slack/Discord/Spotify), git projects, photos

HUD:
- Countdown timer (green to yellow to red)
- Warning text when under 10s remaining
- Round end shows kill time or Echo survived with system threat
